{
  "stem": "3341.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- the children, specially the younger ones-- were not very happy because, you know, the good life which we had from the-- on the country town was-- was very satisfying.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- we were the number one family, maybe, there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had-- I remember then I had the first soccer ball.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 1925, to have a soccer ball was already a sensation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and we had a huge property, because we had a-- a huge garden behind the-- the house, and a big yard, because we sold also building materials and all the other things which normally the other shops didn't have.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we used to have the biggest yard and the biggest garden in town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whenever I wanted to have a-- a soccer match, so I got the whole village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The children would have come from everywhere just to play with a real, proper soccer ball.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was a satisfying life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, when we had to move, because after all, as a child we didn't have any authoration or possibility, so we moved to the big town.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember then I wasn't very happy because it was completely different lifestyle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, the-- the people in every major city consider country people like a country people, you know, that's not very respectable.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I settled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had to settle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I continued my-- my first class of [NON-ENGLISH], which is the high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In European countries the high school is called [NON-ENGLISH], all right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was enrolled in the [NON-ENGLISH], which was a very big change because the children of the-- of the big city-- were all so different.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't the country type of a life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I settled quite well.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
